"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"### Important Equations\\n\\n* Net operating income (NOI)\\n  * yearly rents - yearly expenses \\n    * (account for insurance, tax, & maintenance)\\n* Capitalization rate (rate of return)\\n  * NOI ÷ purchase price \\n* Maximum Allowable offer (MAO)\\n  * ARV x 70% - repair costs\\n* Return of investment (ROI)\\n  * Yearly profit - money invested \\n    * yearly profit = cash flow\\n    * money invested = down payment, closing, rehab, holding, etc.\\n* 1% Rule\\n  * If a property will rent for 1% of the price you paid for it, it’s likely to be cash flow positive. Look for areas that have lots of properties that meet the 1% rule\\n* 75% of ARV\\n  * I want my total expenses for a property (acquisition + rehab) to add up to 75% of what the property will appraise for when finished. \\n\\n### Napkin Method\\n\\n* Rent\\n* Mortgage\\n* Tax\\n* Insurance\\n* Property Management Fees\",\"timestamp\":1638120087,\"title\":\"real estate\"},\"digest\":\"bIarlRlrqhKTdYnrKB-cumgXETBZuSRu_61_5J7gc7o\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x4a1df6A28aBb6694F8cbd418c491271bF67e3a8C\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Ecn9Yol9y_vKFZLQY1GOIFDphjCFyLmS1rT_Po61VGc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"IUkv4yrlnKLT1z3Dr_RyrouTq8f3hqDje0aodQ5t_x8\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"t8OHrq8BKqfLUh7I_VRI9jZNsOzrKznHR_vXt-sDubIX_Yp46LLfkDT4pTw93mDgkiQLnvo_n6raH4GF2EaVAg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x584755c631972873fb8ff8c7d44690fe180a04569d3f25e2bec8dbcb6676655c563600b94100b01c11ab140172c22558f860cf2569a358f0a55a1846326d45c91c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Ecn9Yol9y_vKFZLQY1GOIFDphjCFyLmS1rT_Po61VGc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"IUkv4yrlnKLT1z3Dr_RyrouTq8f3hqDje0aodQ5t_x8\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{}